snippet.title: Saving Prompts | EP12 | Power Up Minute
snippet.description:
Learn how to save, reuse, and share your favorite prompts in this quick Power Up Minute. Discover prompt bookmarking, gallery organization, and team sharing features for enhanced productivity

Unlock new possibilities for collaboration and productivity with Copilot agents. Click the link below to join the Power Up cohort and be part of the growing community:
 
https://aka.ms/PowerUp_Ref_Min
 
And don't forget to connect with peers on the Power Up LinkedIn Group below:
 
https://aka.ms/PowerUpProgram/LI
